        {
            "title": "全日收市︱連跌5日 恒指跌137點報23462點 九倉、太古績後齊受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午市先挫後收復部份失地，卻未能擺脫五連跌的狀況；兩隻綜合企業股九倉(00004)與太古(00019)績後齊受壓。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：九倉官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-174303_source-web_00004-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九倉官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-174303_source-web_00004-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：九倉官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早稍為高開16點後，原本只在10天線(最新約為23565點)升或跌百多點爭持，午後初段卻現明顯跌勢，跌幅最多擴大至401點，低見23198點，連20天線(最新約為23337點)也失守，隨後開始陸續收復失地，於20天線失而復得，但卻受制10天線。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報23462點，跌137點或0.58%；5日累計共跌907點或3.72%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數今日明顯跑輸，收跌97點或1.67%，報5747點；國企指數跌41點或0.48%，報8640點。主板成交進一步縮減至2338.33億元，較昨天再少逾400億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14773845-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c5%e6%97%a5-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c137%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123462%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b9%9d%e5%80%89%e3%80%81%e5%a4%aa%e5%8f%a4%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 16:20:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
